{"tid":417263,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 究竟係邊個提出進化論","createTime":"2017-09-28T13:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T10:30:39.000Z","uid":48670,"like":1,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9b4606bc1bb7d53b146409233cbdd101ffab3a","tid":417263,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :達文西<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :達爾文<br />\n<br />\n我明明記得係達文西<br />\n但又有人講係達爾文<br />\n定係兩個係同一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ea099839cc88923703db3ceb0d91d1a20ca25a","tid":417263,"uid":2419,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"唔好笑呀 過主啦"},{"pid":"175a3c47e449e88e9ab4cafdacaac79a1d201d1c","tid":417263,"uid":27129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719f1168c3bd9a90d54f46c5304aeb9f22074c73","tid":417263,"uid":82829,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好笑呀 過主啦</blockquote><br />\n唔好怪樓主啦 其實佢仲係小學生黎 <br />\n<br />\n我係佢表哥 唔係好親個隻 <br />\n<br />\n佢有少少低智個d唔好講啦 <br />\n<br />\n佢讀特殊學校個d都無謂提 <br />\n<br />\n不過大家放過佢啦 佢仲係讀緊小三 <br />\n<br />\n佢老豆老母都好辛苦 要照顧佢 <br />\n<br />\n佢細細個已經食雞唔食雞皮 食橙食埋橙皮 <br />\n<br />\n我代佢係呢度向大家道歉一聲"},{"pid":"c8ba6f51d7eb0d28fdb663c5257cbbc791f7fae5","tid":417263,"uid":75737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"冇進化論 得演化論"},{"pid":"453d166b4af03a9666646799e3680aeb35edd68f","tid":417263,"uid":138762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T04:23:56.000Z","msg":"究竟巴菲特同菲比斯邊個先係游泳健將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa7a356186b82eec7d43a03c09660f967a15438","tid":417263,"uid":98755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc